\begin_layout Standard
The STDP parameters we used were previously measured experimentally in vivo
 in the STDP learning paradigm (
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citealp
key "Abbott:2000gg"

\end_inset

).
 In our learning paradigm dopamine gates synaptic learning which is to say
 synaptic change cannot occurr in the absence of dopamine.
 We have used a general model of dopamine gated STDP learning (
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citealp
key "Izhikevich:2004ul"

\end_inset

).
 
\end_layout

